title: A Series of Unfortunate Events - Logic Game (Requested) [h33t][W
description:
A Series of Unfortunate Events.

Tropical Dream: Underwater Odyssey is an upcoming game from 

award-winning mobile and now PC game developer, Digital Chocolate 

(creators of Tower Bloxx).

Tropical Dream: Underwater Odyssey is about a girl named Megan who 

wants to build a house in a tropical paradise. To earn money, she dives 

deep into the reefs to take underwater pictures of fishes and sell the 

pictures to tourists.

The game mixes together a splash of an arcade game with a sprinkle of 

hidden object elements. There are also two paradise-flavored 

mini-games; match three and a memory game, in which the player frees 

the fishes. And, the beautiful, animated fishes actually smile and pose 

for you as you take their pictures (cool)! Tropical Dream features 75 

levels of game play and is a very well-produced and unique game to 

play.

A Series of Unfortunate Events, *OBG* logic puzzle game by 

BigFish/Oberon
A Series of Unfortunate Events is here and it&#039;s your job to halt Count 

Olaf&#039;s trail-of-terror. Stop Count Olaf&#039;s unmentionable HORRORS with 

fire, snake bites, leeches, and other wieldy machinations in this 

fascinating game of logic and deductive reasoning. Too awful of a game? 

Too scary and dark? Too spine-tingling a premise? Well, then, go play 

something cheerier.

You&#039;ve been warned! Do NOT download this game if you can&#039;t stand up to 

Evil!

Stop Count Olaf in his tracks.
Full of spine-tingling terror.
A game of logic and reasoning.
